title: Solent Plastics 60 Litre Heavy Duty Red Storage Boxes - 5 Pack (60 x 40 x 32 cm)
features: Solent Plastics 60 Litre Heavy Duty Colour Coded Attached Lid Containers Available In 5 Colours 5 X Red Spkm320
description: 60 Litre Heavy Duty Colour Coded Attached Lid Containers - Available in 5 Colours! Attached Lid Containers offer unrivalled quality and price. Now available in 5 colours! Ideal for when colour coded storage is required. Made from Virgin Polypropylene, an unrivalled materials handling solution. Excellent Load Capacity of 35kg per container / 140kg stacked capacity. Temperature Range of -20 to + 70 Degrees Celsius. Improved lid design with lock in points to assist with stable stacking. Ribbed label area on ends and lid for labels and barcodes. Slightly ribbed base for added strength. Lids can be secured at either end and middle of lid with security seals. Stackable when full, nestable when empty.
